r t BC-POMPEII-TOURISM0404-C     04-03 2892
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-POMPEII-TOURISM0404-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Tourism takes its toll
 &HT;    By Mike Toner
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   POMPEII, Italy _ In 62 A.D. it was devastated by an earthquake.
