<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-03 13:27 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5638 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u k BC-JACOBY-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      04-03 0933
