shorter and shorter. Rumors persist that the USGA is considering
taking the juice out of golf balls; that might be just what Augusta
needs. Golfers (including Jack Nicklaus) and Augusta officials
discuss the issue. (Bunn, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 30.
