   BBN-REDS-OPENER _ CINCINNATI _ It's Opening Day and more than
55,000 fans will jam into Cinergy Field. Color from the plaza
outside Cinergy to the red seats behind Ken Griffey Jr. in center
field to the clubhouse. What was the atmosphere like on Junior
Griffey's first day as a Red? (Vinella, Dayton Daily News). 18.
WITH PHOTOS.
