   FBN-DRAFT-DAYNE _ Wisconsin's Ron Dayne won the 1999 Heisman
Trophy and rushed for more yards than any player in NCAA history.
But Dayne might be only the fourth running back selected because of
concerns about his weight and speed. (Schlabach, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 14.
