</P>
<P>
   ALAMIN-PROBE _ The FBI is still trying to figure out who helped
Jamil Al-Amin, the former Black Panther known as H. Rap Brown, in
Alabama. The mayor of White Hall, four Muslims stopped before
Al-Amin was captured, and others are being investigated, the FBI
says. Tests from the Mercedes may help narrow the list of suspects.
(Longa, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 15.
