</P>
<P>
   AL-AMIN-BROTHER _ ATLANTA _ Characterizing the atmosphere
surrounding the Jamil Al-Amin case as ``the frenzy of a lynch
mob,'' his brother granted a wide-ranging interview Monday in an
effort to provide some balance. Ed Brown, 58, criticized Sheriff
Jackie Barrett and others for creating a poisoned atmosphere in
which it may be difficult for Al-Amin to get a fair trial. (Gentry,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 25. WITH PHOTO.
