BILL GOODYKOONTZ. Story will move in the ``E'' category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
TV-GOODY-FALCONE (Undated) - A few things`Falcon` is not: a
miniseries, a `Sopranos` knock-off, a mob story. According to its
executive producers, anyway. Casual observers will be forgiven if
the CBS drama seems like all of those things. After all, eight
episodes will be shown almost consecutively; the success of the HBO
series is what got it on the air; and it's about an FBI agent who
goes undercover in the Mafia. But why quibble? Because here's
something Falcone definitely is: Worth watching. By BILL
GOODYKOONTZ. Story moved in the ``E'' category. &QL;
