<HEADLINE>
RIVALS RENEW CALLS TO BREAKUP MICROSOFT
</HEADLINE>
   (With MICROSOFT-ANTITRUST) 
(nk) 
 By JOHN MARKOFF and MATT RICHTEL   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   SAN FRANCISCO _ Reinvigorated by Monday's ruling in the
